------------------Soccer Playbook------------------

-Installation:
	If you don't want the source:
	Download the Win32 Binaries Zip
	Extract to the folder of your choice.
	Run the Exe

I'm not gonna explain how to compile from the source at this time. If you wanna go for it, grab SDL from http://libsdl.org/ and compile with compiler of your choice. I've tested it on Ubuntu with G++ as well as Windows 7 with VS2010. Both compile fine if SDL is set up correctly.